<P>
Column; Infobox 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA080494-0062 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 066728 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
August 4, 1994, Thursday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
OC Live; Page 4; OC Live 
</P>
