</P>
<P>
 These two harmonizing sisters recently stepped off the ladder to big-time 
country stardom and made a bluegrass-flavored, highly traditional album for an 
independent label. The Sweethearts play the Coach House on Tuesday, Aug. 9. 
Gina Quartaro, a promising local, will open. (714) 496-8930. 
</P>
