<DOCID> 066744 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
August 4, 1994, Thursday, Southland Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 13; Column 1; National Desk 
</P>
