 Ryan O'Neil of Camarillo fired rounds of 76 and 79 to win the overall title in 
Ventura County Junior Golf Assn.'s Saticoy Junior championship at Saticoy 
Country Club in Camarillo. 
</P>
<P>
 O'Neil, who attends Rio Mesa High, edged Tyler Satchwell of Ventura by one 
shot. Scott Christenson of Agoura shot 86 to win the 14-15 division, and Jeff 
Coburn of Ojai shot 84 to win the 13-and-under division. 
</P>
<P>
 Alexandria Erlandson of Camarillo shot 84 to win the girls' division by one 
shot over Jill Kaopua of Oxnard. 
</P>
