waived by the St. Louis Cardinals. Murphy was 4-3 with two saves in 50 relief 
appearances for the Cardinals with a 3.79 ERA in 40 1/3 innings. . . . Montreal 
Manager Felipe Alou flew home to the Dominican Republic to attend the funeral 
of his father, Jose Rojas, 89. Bench coach Tim Johnson took over as manager 
Wednesday and is expected to do so again today. 
