<P>
 UnionFed Financial Corp.: The Brea parent of Union Federal Bank on Wednesday 
reported a loss of $26.5 million for its latest fiscal year, which ended June 
30. That compared to a loss of $32.1 million for the same period the previous 
year.For the fourth quarter, UnionFed reported a loss of $9.8 million, compared 
