regulatory capital requirements and is subject to increased monitoring by the 
federal Office of Thrift Supervision. UnionFed said it has hired Keefe, 
Bruyette & Woods Inc. as a financial adviser, subject to OTS approval, to help 
it formulate a capital restoration plan. 
